WITH ch AS (SELECT ch.dim_chr_abr, ch.dim_abr, ch.DATASET_ID db_nm, ch.chr_data_typ chr_data_typ FROM metadata.V_EX_FE_DB_DIM_CHR ch WHERE ch.DATASET_ID = '34202' And (( ( ch.dim_chr_abr IN ( 'PRD_DSC_SHORT_EN_PL','PRD_KEY' ) ) and ch.dim_abr='PRD') or ( ( ch.dim_chr_abr IN ( 'PRDC_LVL_TYP','PRDC_DET_LVL','CSTM_300763' ) ) and ch.dim_abr='PRDC') or ( ( ch.dim_chr_abr IN ( 'M_MKT_DISP_NAME','MRKT_KEY' ) ) and ch.dim_abr='MRKT') ) ), itm_dtl AS (SELECT * FROM metadata.V_EX_FE_FM_QRY_ITM_DTL WHERE DATASET_ID = '34202' and dim_abr in ('PRD','PRDC','MRKT') ) SELECT ch.dim_abr dim_abr, sort_ch.srt_dim_chr_abr sort_chr_id, sort_ch.dim_abr sort_chr_dim_id, a.dim_chr_abr chr_id, a.query_subject, a.query_item_col_nm, a.cat_nm, a.sch_nm, a.tbl_als, a.lov_tbl_nm, a.enrichment_resolution_type enrichment_resolution_type,a.dynamic_query dynamic_query, (select b.query_item_col_nm from itm_dtl b where sort_ch.srt_dim_chr_abr = b.dim_chr_abr AND sort_ch.dim_abr = b.dim_abr AND sort_ch.DATASET_ID = b.DATASET_ID) sort_query_item_col_nm, (select b.lov_tbl_nm from itm_dtl b where sort_ch.srt_dim_chr_abr = b.dim_chr_abr AND sort_ch.dim_abr = b.dim_abr AND sort_ch.DATASET_ID = b.DATASET_ID) sort_lov_table, ch.chr_data_typ chr_data_typ FROM ch left outer join itm_dtl a ON ( CH.dim_chr_abr = a.dim_chr_abr AND CH.dim_abr = a.dim_abr AND CH.db_nm = a.DATASET_ID ) left outer join metadata.V_EX_FE_DB_DIM_CHR sort_ch ON ( CH.dim_chr_abr = sort_ch.dim_chr_abr AND CH.dim_abr = sort_ch.dim_abr AND CH.db_nm = sort_ch.DATASET_ID )
